# AI API 成本归因规范

## 核心原则

每次调用外部 AI API（Claude / FLUX.1 / ElevenLabs / Kling）后，**必须立即**将实际成本写入 `generation_jobs` 表，不得只在内存中累计。

## 各 API 成本计算

```typescript
// apps/worker/src/lib/cost-calculator.ts
const CNY_PER_USD = 7.2  // 定期更新汇率

export const CostCalculator = {
  claude: (inputTokens: number, outputTokens: number) =>
    ((inputTokens * 0.000003 + outputTokens * 0.000015) * CNY_PER_USD),

  flux1: () => 0.04 * CNY_PER_USD,         // $0.04/张

  elevenLabs: (chars: number) =>
    (chars * 0.00018 * CNY_PER_USD),        // $0.00018/字符

  kling: (durationSec: number) =>
    (durationSec * 0.05 * CNY_PER_USD),     // $0.05/秒（Pro）
}
```

## 写入模板（每个 Job 必须实现）

```typescript
async function processStoryboardJob(job: Job<StoryboardJobData>) {
  const jobRecord = await db.insert(generationJobs).values({
    projectId: job.data.projectId,
    type: 'storyboard',
    status: 'running',
    startedAt: new Date(),
  }).returning().then(r => r[0])

  try {
    const [imageUrl] = await flux1.generate(scene.visualPrompt)
    const cost = CostCalculator.flux1()

    // ✅ 每张图完成立即写入成本
    await db.update(generationJobs)
      .set({ aiCostCny: Math.round(cost * 100), status: 'done', finishedAt: new Date() })
      .where(eq(generationJobs.id, jobRecord.id))

    // ✅ 累加到项目总成本
    await db.update(projects)
      .set({ totalCostCny: sql`${projects.totalCostCny} + ${Math.round(cost * 100)}` })
      .where(eq(projects.id, job.data.projectId))
  } catch (err) {
    await db.update(generationJobs)
      .set({ status: 'failed', finishedAt: new Date() })
      .where(eq(generationJobs.id, jobRecord.id))
    throw err
  }
}
```

## 毛利率监控告警

```typescript
// 当某个项目的实际成本 > 估算成本 × 1.5 时，发告警
const COST_OVERRUN_THRESHOLD = 1.5

if (actualCostCny > estimatedCostCny * COST_OVERRUN_THRESHOLD) {
  await alertOps(`项目 ${projectId} 成本超支：估算 ¥${estimatedCostCny/100}，实际 ¥${actualCostCny/100}`)
}
```
